Invocation Name: music dreams u. s. a. radio
des:
"Music Dreams USA Worldwide Radio is a professional internet streaming radio station. With a worldwide listening audience. We got the world covered with the best mix of the 80s and 90s with some amazing music shows mixed in-between. We are you home for Vox Sports and Football Phanatics as we cover the NFL. 

We offer a variety of services worldwide check them out here: www.musicdreamsusa.com 
Music Dreams Worldwide Radio supports upcoming established or upcoming artists and companies worldwide. Whatever you request is we got you covered! Please send your requests to: info.musicdreamsusa@gmail.com. Are you hooked yet? Ready to check out our amazing music? Listen Live Worldwide: www.musicdreamsusa.com or simply ask Alexa to play Music Dreams USA 

For rates and dates please email us at info.musicdreamsusa@gmail.com

Thank you for checking us out and we look forward to working with you......."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
